1025
01:05:16,600 --> 01:05:17,800
Papai!

1026
01:05:18,440 --> 01:05:19,480
Papai!

1027
01:05:33,240 --> 01:05:34,280
Eles voltaram.

1028
01:05:37,040 --> 01:05:38,240
Bela!

1029
01:05:39,280 --> 01:05:41,680
Tudo bem, papai.
Eu voltei.

1030
01:05:43,280 --> 01:05:45,840
