1171
01:15:31,760 --> 01:15:34,160
Farei o que quiser!
Qualquer coisa!

1172
01:15:47,360 --> 01:15:48,840
Saia daqui.

1173
01:15:50,080 --> 01:15:51,080
Fera!

1174
01:15:52,160 --> 01:15:53,120
Bela.

1175
01:16:02,040 --> 01:16:02,840
Bela.

1176
01:16:08,600 --> 01:16:09,880
